1
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:18,190
<i>"Vow to You" - Liu Yuning</i>

2
00:00:18,190 --> 00:00:20,260
♫ <i>The flames illuminate the dark night</i> ♫

3
00:00:20,260 --> 00:00:24,180
♫ <i>Silences surrounds the world</i> ♫

4
00:00:24,180 --> 00:00:25,950
♫ <i>The starlight fades away</i> ♫

5
00:00:25,950 --> 00:00:29,520
♫ <i>The living stands in fear</i> ♫

6
00:00:29,520 --> 00:00:32,480
♫ <i>Wake me up from this nightmare</i> ♫

7
00:00:32,480 --> 00:00:35,620
♫ <i>I see through your blushing</i> ♫

8
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:41,720
♫ <i>The thought of you in this world urges me to make a decision</i> ♫

9
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:44,380
♫ <i>Entrusted to me the gale and flame</i> ♫

10
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:47,080
♫ <i>This farewell leaves me in pain</i> ♫

11
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:49,840
♫ <i>I am fearless when I take a drive into the abyss for you</i> ♫

12
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:53,100
♫ <i>I'll defend death to be with you</i> ♫

13
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:58,500
♫ <i>Heaven and Earth resonates with the mountains and the rivers</i> ♫

14
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:01,500
♫ <i>The world is untamed and unbridled</i> ♫

15
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:04,660
♫ <i>Come what may</i> ♫

16
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:10,000
♫ <i>I am willing to risk my life for you</i> ♫

17
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,840
♫ <i>Let's go stargazing tomorrow</i> ♫

18
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:18,960
♫ <i>I'll never regret my lifelong vow to you</i> ♫

19
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:44,980
<i>[The Starry Love]
[Adapted from "The Starry Love" by Yi Du Jun Hua]</i>

20
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:47,980
<i>[Episode 16]</i>

21
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:50,700
<i>Drink up!</i>

22
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:51,600
I feel much better.

23
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:54,880
Sir. Don't move! Sir.

24
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:57,560
Sir, these acupuncture needles are amazing.

25
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,560
That's right. Join us.

26
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:02,130
Where are you guys going?

27
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:04,620
- Buy a sword.
- Grab a bite. Go for a show.

28
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,380
It's rare for us to visit the Mortal Realm. We want to take a stroll.

29
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:13,133
That's right.

30
00:02:13,133 --> 00:02:14,100
Great.

31
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:16,980
Although I'm a princess, I've lived in the palace for most of my life.

32
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:18,920
I rarely have the opportunity to enjoy the bustling city and market.

33
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,920
Let's go together.

34
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:24,840
- Your Highness, this is...
- Su Shui, you can stay here and tell the warriors to drink up.

35
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,820
- I...
- It's rare for you guys to come here.

36
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:29,720
I should be a good host to you all. Don't mention it.

37
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:32,000
- I...
- I don't think I'll follow.

38
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,133
Let's go!

39
00:02:33,133 --> 00:02:35,720
- Don't be courteous. It's my treat.
- Your Highness.

40
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,760
- We should stop.
- I have a date with Sushui. Why don't you two go?
<i>[Jufu Inn]</i>

41
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,240
Your Highness.

42
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,973
Hurry up.

43
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:44,433
Let's go.

44
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,741
<i>I promised Tan that I'd hide her tracks.</i>

45
00:02:51,741 --> 00:02:54,660
<i>But... But what should I do?</i>

46
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:56,100
The market is huge.

47
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:58,250
Kui'er, what do you want to buy?

48
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:00,820
It's rare for me to be outside. I feel like buying everything.

49
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:03,260
I think I'll buy some accessories.

50
00:03:10,250 --> 00:03:11,800
<i>[Missing Person]</i>

51
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:15,280
<i>Empyrean?</i>

52
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,861
<i>Why are there portraits of him on the streets?</i>

53
00:03:17,861 --> 00:03:20,000
<i>Tan'er and other people have been searching for soul shards for over a year.</i>

54
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,201
<i>I assume they were the ones who put up the notice.</i>

55
00:03:22,201 --> 00:03:25,610
<i>I must make sure Chaofeng doesn't see it.</i>

56
00:03:25,610 --> 00:03:27,500
Kui'er, check this out.

57
00:03:34,170 --> 00:03:35,460
<i>[Missing Person]</i>

58
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:40,720
What's the matter?

59
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:45,020
I sprained my waist when I was doing acupuncture for them.

60
00:03:45,020 --> 00:03:47,170
I have to do a stretch.

61
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:52,360
<i>This seems like Shaodian Youqin.</i>

62
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,160
<i>Seems like my guess was correct.</i>

63
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:57,980
<i>Not only has Kui'er met Yetan, but she also found out about the fire demon.</i>

64
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,440
Sushui said they'd perform a show soon, right?

65
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:03,940
Let's go and watch it. Go and find a stage.

66
00:04:03,940 --> 00:04:05,320
I'll look for you guys later.

67
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:07,253
Watch a show?

68
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:11,020
<i>She's spending so much effort hiding his portrait from me.</i>

69
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:13,970
<i>Is she trying to hide their tracks?</i>

70
00:04:13,970 --> 00:04:15,533
All right.

71
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:29,340
<i>Excellent!</i>

72
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:30,760
<i>Brilliant!</i>

73
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:33,180
<i>Amazing!</i>

74
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,773
Kui'er!

75
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:41,380
- Has it already started? Sit down.
- Excellent!

76
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:46,420
<i>Excellent!</i>

77
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:54,480
<i>Brilliant! Awesome!</i>

78
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,541
Sit down! You're blocking the people behind us.

79
00:04:56,541 --> 00:04:57,660
I can't see anything, either.

80
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:59,020
You guys are too tall.

81
00:04:59,020 --> 00:04:59,980
- Sit down!
- Another one!

82
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:03,260
- You're too tall! Sit down!
- Excellent!

83
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:07,140
I've watched this before. Why don't we walk around?

84
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:08,740
Let's go. Time to go.

85
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:11,480
- Let's go. Time to go.
- Excellent!

86
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,800
Let's go!

87
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,710
Let's go and buy some clothes. The designs they have here are great.
<i> [Clothes Shop]</i>

88
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:23,180
The designs they have here are great.
<i>[Clothes Shop]</i>

89
00:05:23,180 --> 00:05:25,100
Let's go.

90
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:28,400
- Haichao. Join us. Come on.
- I...

91
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:30,593
Hurry.

92
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:33,420
You'll only know if they're good after you try them on.

93
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,840
I'll wait for you guys at the entrance.

94
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,673
Go now.

95
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:44,240
Hurry up.

96
00:05:52,410 --> 00:05:53,660
<i>[Missing Person]</i>

97
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:04,580
<i>[Clothes Shop]</i>

98
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,733
Kui'er.

99
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,600
You look nice.

100
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:20,560
But I think black looks better on you two.

101
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,540
Why don't you guys go and get changed again?

102
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:23,720
Sorry about that.

103
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,970
I'll wait here for you two.

104
00:06:25,970 --> 00:06:27,673
Go now.

105
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:48,320
<i>Luckily, there's not a single portrait of him here.</i>

106
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:51,650
Have you selected the dishes?

107
00:06:51,650 --> 00:06:53,600
Human food is long overdue.

108
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,100
All of them are great.

109
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:57,850
You should select them.

110
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:59,520
<i>[Menu]</i>

111
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:05,360
I'm sure you're exhausted after the long day.

112
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,640
However, I've never seen you in such a good mood before.

113
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:11,060
I... I've always been in a good mood.

114
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,140
What about you?

115
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:14,600
You've spent the entire day shopping around with me. You must be exhausted.

116
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:19,560
I think we should return to our inn and rest once we finish our snacks.

117
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:25,640
<i>In the past, I've deceived her about many things, no matter if it was intentional or not.</i>

118
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:28,741
<i>I never expected her to try to deceive me now.</i>

119
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:34,980
Kui'er, ever since we arrived at the Mortal Realm, you've become gentler and more considerate.

120
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:38,000
Now, you're even serving me tea.

121
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:40,460
You only served me tea when I was hurt in the past.

122
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:43,080
If you like the days we spend in the Mortal Realm,

123
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:45,880
I'll make tea for you every day in the future.

124
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:49,533
Forget it.

125
00:07:49,533 --> 00:07:52,560
The Mortal Realm is huge. I'm exhausted from all the fun.

126
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,880
I still have official affairs to complete.

127
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,940
I'll gather intelligence about our enemy later.

128
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:58,500
There's no rush.

129
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:03,300
I don't want to leave, either.

130
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:07,120
However, drinking tea is the only thing we do here.

131
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,100
It's no fun.

132
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:20,160
I'll stay if we have something fun to do.

133
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:23,720
What do you mean by that?

134
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:41,973
Sir.

135
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,350
Here's your liquor.

136
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:51,300
Time to have some fun!

137
00:08:54,620 --> 00:08:57,420
I told you to look after your body when we were in the Void Realm. I'm sure it was tough on you.

138
00:08:57,420 --> 00:09:00,370
Since we have some fine liquor today, I shall drink with you.

139
00:09:00,370 --> 00:09:01,933
Here.

140
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:12,273
Cheers.

141
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:20,530
This liquor is excellent, indeed.

142
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:26,960
I'll have another cup.

143
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:32,653
Cheers.

144
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:39,473
It's so good.

145
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:42,190
Let's have another cup.

146
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:44,140
Drink up.

147
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:52,960
Here. You should drink up.

148
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:20,453
We finally got Princess Qingkui drunk.

149
00:10:20,453 --> 00:10:23,360
Kui'er wanted to get us drunk.

150
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:26,840
You're the worst at deceiving people.

151
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:31,600
I would've continued to act with you if it wasn't an emergency.

152
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:34,360
We should drop the act. Let's get down to business.

153
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:38,080
We need to head to Yuewo Village and kill Shaodian Youqin.

154
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:42,740
Kui'er is caught in between the two clans.

155
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:45,420
That's why she tried to hide his tracks from me.

156
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:49,800
But according to royal father, the one who kills Shaodian Youqin will be the next crown prince.

157
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:52,180
This is my best opportunity.

158
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:54,150
I cannot give up now.

159
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:57,153
Kui'er,

160
00:10:57,820 --> 00:11:00,170
I have no choice but to let you down.

161
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:11,593
Sir, I thought you were going to let her down.

162
00:11:11,593 --> 00:11:14,480
Why are you carrying her? Are you heading to Yuewo Village with her?

163
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:16,520
I'll send her back to the inn first.

164
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:18,020
She's finally passed out.

165
00:11:18,020 --> 00:11:19,480
We mustn't waste this opportunity.

166
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,940
Speed is of the essence here.

167
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:23,950
Sir, we should be quick!

168
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:33,333
Dear, Wang Ergou helped us out when we were young.

169
00:11:33,333 --> 00:11:36,380
Now, he's in trouble. How could we not help him out?

170
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,300
I already tried my best to be as thrifty as possible.

171
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:40,260
Do you think we don't need to pay for our child's education?

172
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:42,000
Don't tell me you want me to get back the money from him.

173
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,120
- Go and get the money right now.
- No, I won't.

174
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:46,000
- Are you going or not?
- I said I'm not going.

175
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,440
You're not going? Forget it, then.

176
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,833
I'll leave.

177
00:11:48,833 --> 00:11:50,333
Yuehong!

178
00:11:50,333 --> 00:11:52,113
What?

179
00:11:52,113 --> 00:11:54,200
I-I'm sorry.

180
00:11:57,800 --> 00:12:00,980
Dear, are you no longer angry at me?

181
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:02,653
Let's go.

182
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,220
Right now, the villagers of Yuewo Village are out to get him.

183
00:12:09,220 --> 00:12:11,500
The voidwalkers have been involved. Qingkui has been involved, too.

184
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:14,340
This is getting worse and worse.

185
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:18,700
Heartless Shaodian, why is it so difficult to save you?

186
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:21,300
If so, what do you plan to do with the voidwalkers?

187
00:12:21,300 --> 00:12:23,233
The voidwalkers?

188
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:28,481
Void Third Prince already found out that we'd descended to this realm.

189
00:12:28,481 --> 00:12:30,080
They've sent their scouts here.

190
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,460
I almost bumped into them today.

191
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:35,620
Right now, we have to persuade Fiery to leave this place.

192
00:12:35,620 --> 00:12:39,920
And then we should find the other two soul shards and revive the Empyrean soon.

193
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:44,433
I'm afraid we can't keep a low profile.

194
00:12:55,075 --> 00:12:56,975
<i>[Missing Person]</i>

195
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:01,740
You guys were the ones who put up this notice?

196
00:13:01,740 --> 00:13:04,500
We were just thinking that since we'd already found Fiery,

197
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:07,340
we should retrieve the other two soul shards as soon as possible.

198
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:11,020
Thus, we put up notices with his portrait all along the way.

199
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:16,021
We used bounty to lure those who sought soul shards before.

200
00:13:16,021 --> 00:13:19,000
We wanted them to provide leads to us.

201
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:21,520
The voidwalkers are in the Mortal Realm now.

202
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:26,100
If they discover this portrait, they'll find out that your brother is in trouble.

203
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:28,140
How many of them did you guys put up?

204
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,140
How many?

205
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:30,900
We spent the entire night putting them up.

206
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:32,140
There are at least hundreds of them.

207
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:36,140
What? We've posted them on all of the main paths in the Mortal and Beast Realms.

208
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,480
Hurry then. Go and remove them!

209
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,780
Hurry up! Split up!

210
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:43,500
- I...
- Just go already! Go!

211
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:45,433
You...

212
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:48,060
Sister-in-law, leave this to us.

213
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:51,280
You should stay here and persuade Fiery.

214
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:53,340
I'll join him.

215
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,300
That's right, Sister-in-law.

216
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:57,260
Youqin became strange after you left.

217
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:59,080
At first, he just locked himself in the room.

218
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:01,240
He was making something in the room.

219
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:06,960
Just now, when I passed by Yuewo Village, I saw him watching an argument between a couple.

220
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:09,440
You should check on him.

221
00:14:12,875 --> 00:14:14,425
<i>[Missing Person]</i>

222
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:25,020
Sir, please.

223
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:28,200
- Here you go.
- All right.

224
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,940
I'm starving.

225
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:33,260
- Bring some tea!
- Got it!

226
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:39,840
Shaodian Youqin, not only did you steal Tan Tan from me, but you're also the reason I have to run around.

227
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,500
I'll beat you up. I'll beat you up.

228
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:44,660
Beat you up!

229
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:46,960
Beat you up!

230
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,993
Di Lanjue?

231
00:14:58,300 --> 00:15:00,140
Can you do me a favor?

232
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:12,970
That hateful Qingheng, why did he put it up so high?

233
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,680
Higher.

234
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,430
Do I need to go higher?

235
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:45,380
♫ <i>I have this sudden yearning to hear you say, "I like you"</i> ♫

236
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:48,620
♫ <i>How do I put this feeling into words and foreshadow my little excitements?</i> ♫

237
00:15:48,620 --> 00:15:52,939
♫ <i>Maybe our superstitious of love is sweet</i> ♫

238
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:56,920
♫ <i>I sink into your tender gaze like a river of love</i> ♫

239
00:15:56,920 --> 00:16:01,019
♫ <i>Cherishing each other and just talk about anything</i> ♫

240
00:16:01,019 --> 00:16:02,280
<i>A'Cai?</i>

241
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:05,139
♫ <i>You say we should stargaze together</i> ♫

242
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:08,280
Are you okay?

243
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:09,633
You...

244
00:16:09,633 --> 00:16:13,360
